snippet.title: Monsters, Inc. - GBC Longplay/Walkthrough #3 [720p]
snippet.description:
Gameboy Color: Monsters, Inc.

Rating: 3/5

Pretty good game, has a lot of charm and follows the movie very closely, even has some cutscenes. Controls could be a bit better and sometimes it gets too difficult because of that. Overall, not bad.
